I just switched from hammer to axe and am a total convert. For positionals, the Evernight/Arctic rift rear is great in both PvE and RvR,<br>
------------<br>
<br>
So is conq/sledge, you didn't use it or something?<br>
<br>
The other benefit of hammer is conq in itself.  It's got a 23 second snare now.  For assist groups, you know what that means.  You dont have to have a PF person in the crew, and/or you dont have to wait for it.  The first time you land conq that person's not gonna go very far.  Skalds are an assist class in groups of 8..and conq makes them a good assister.<br>
<br>
50 sword for Rag is another good assist style, high damage (but no snare).<br>
<br>
-Dane<br>
